640
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:24,210
♫Gatherings, separations, joy and sorrow, the myriad facets of life♫

641
00:37:19,830 --> 00:37:21,390
She's grieving the loss of her son

642
00:37:21,390 --> 00:37:22,710
