644
00:37:24,420 --> 00:37:32,250
♫Looking back at the fleeting snow and wind, I have no regrets♫

645
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:31,320
When she wakes up,

646
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,780
just take good care of her.

