659
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,120
It's my fault.

660
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:22,110
♫Warm stovetops and green film in wine, like an eternal farewell♫

661
00:39:19,180 --> 00:39:20,640
I hope there will come a day

662
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,060
